The paper deals with controlling swarms of agents, which is a topic that falls under the category of Multi-Agent Systems (cs.MA). The use of global broadcast signals and lack of information on absolute location and orientation suggest that the paper may also fall under the categories of Robotics (cs.RO) and Systems and Control (cs.SY). The paper also involves the use of algorithms and decision-making processes, which are topics that fall under the categories of Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI) and Social and Information Networks (cs.SI).
